Name: StringValue
Description: The code term as it appears in the controlled vocabulary

Name: OtherValue
Description: If the value of the string is "Other" or the equivalent from the controlled vocabulary, this attribute can provide a more specific value not found in the controlled vocabulary.

Name: ControlledVocabularyCodeListReference
Description: A DDI CodeList representation of the controlled vocabulary that the content was taken from.

Name: ControlledVocabularyURI
Description: Specifies the URI location for the full controlled vocabulary, usually represented in an RDF SKOS or XKOS representation.

Name: ControlledVocabularyInstanceURI
Description: Specifies the identification URI of the term/code within the controlled vocabulary if available.
